{"tid":2074820,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"国安進，法官退 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-06-22T11:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T11:39:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3f08e1d2679305c653918a59373c85d79a5f70","tid":2074820,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200622/20941721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200622%2F20941721%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=2f2af9ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200622%2F20941721%2F&h=2807a6f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200622/20941721/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n国安進，法官退 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200622/large/1592724262_7485.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200622%2Flarge%2F1592724262_7485.jpg&h=3ba565f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔會考慮！裁判官講兩次（唔夠重要？）「唔會考慮」18歲中五男生保釋，認為男生去年11月11日在柴灣道天橋藏有彈簧刀是干犯「嚴格責任罪行」。。。。。。。，法官大人依舊冷酷「唔會考慮」拉他們一把。挽救生命於既倒的俠義，在冷氣開行的法院裏不存在，卻活現在催煙椒氣的街頭，夜間清潔工何先生張開雙臂叫年輕人快啲走、自稱差四個月就51歲的深水埗大叔獲判社會服務令後對記者說，雖然只有小學程度，但知道什麼應該做，「不忍心看着優秀的年輕人犧牲。」這就是公務員顏武周先生（好名字！）說的：「我沒有站出來，是放棄信念的人不斷在後退。」 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}